## gllvmTMB licensing
##
## gllvmTMB is a standalone Template Model Builder (TMB) package for
## stacked-trait, long-format multivariate generalised linear latent
## variable models (GLLVMs). The gllvmTMB-specific code -- the
## multi-trait engine in inst/tmb/gllvmTMB_multi.cpp, the formula
## parser, the 3 x 5 covariance keyword grid, the per-trait response
## families (including ordinal_probit), the diagnostic and extractor
## machinery -- is licensed GPL-3 by Shinichi Nakagawa.
##
## The GPL-3 components listed below were inherited from sdmTMB
## (Anderson et al. 2025) and through sdmTMB from the upstream code
## base of TMB (Kristensen et al. 2016). The body that follows
## describes the upstream provenance of the inherited code, not
## gllvmTMB's own attribution scope.
##
## ----------------------------------------------------------------
